<P><B><A NAME="Summary"></A>1. SUMMARY</B></P>
<P>1.1 This supplementary proof provides responses to various points made in
the Objectors' proofs of evidence related to aspects of the geology and
hydrogeology of the Sellafield site.</P>
<P>1.2 Responses are made to points raised by</P>
<TABLE BORDER="BORDER">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="50"></TD>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="50">i.</TD>
<TD WIDTH="800">Professor Mather (PE/CCC/4 for Cumbria County Council)</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5"></TD>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5">ii.</TD>
<TD WIDTH="800">Dr Green and Dr Western (PE/FOE/1 for Friends of the Earth)</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5"></TD>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5">iii.</TD>
<TD WIDTH="800">Dr Kokelaar (PE/FOE/2 for Friends of the Earth)
</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5"></TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5">iv.</TD>
<TD WIDTH="800">Professor Smythe (PE/FOE/3 for Friends of the Earth)
</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5"></TD>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5">v.</TD>
<TD WIDTH="800">Mr Reeves (PE/FOE/4 for Friends of the Earth)
</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5"></TD>
