instead of measured data (paragraph 2.13);
</TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5"></TD>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="5">iv.</TD>
<TD WIDTH="800">his interpretation of the hydrogeological field tests differs
from that presented by Nirex (paragraphs 2.19 and 2.20); and
</TD></TR>
